ra</a> </span> <span class="meta-author" title="Author"> <i class="icon-user"></i> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://www.gbopera.it/author/michele-curnis/" title="View all posts by Michele Curnis" rel="author">Michele Curnis</a></span> </span> <span class="meta-tags" title="Tags"> <i class="icon-tags"></i> <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/angelo-linzalata/" rel="tag">Angelo Linzalata</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/coro-schola-cantorum-san-gregorio-magno/" rel="tag">Coro Schola Cantorum San Gregorio Magno</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/dario-argento/" rel="tag">Dario Argento</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/dario-di-vietri/" rel="tag">Dario Di Vietri</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/dimitra-theodossiou/" rel="tag">dimitra theodossiou</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/elena-bianchini/" rel="tag">Elena Bianchini</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/ernesto-petti/" rel="tag">Ernesto Petti</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/giuseppe-altomare/" rel="tag">Giuseppe Altomare</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/giuseppe-sabbatini/" rel="tag">Giuseppe Sabbatini</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/giuseppe-verdi/" rel="tag">Giuseppe Verdi</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/macbeth/" rel="tag">Macbeth</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/mauro-rolfi/" rel="tag">Mauro Rolfi</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/opera-lirica/" rel="tag">Opera lirica</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/orchestra-filarmonica-del-piemonte/" rel="tag">Orchestra Filarmonica del Piemonte</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/piero-ceffa/" rel="tag">Piero Ceffa</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/radu-pintillie/" rel="tag">Radu Pintillie</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/teatro-coccia-di-novara/" rel="tag">teatro Coccia di Novara</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/valeria-sepe/" rel="tag">Valeria Sepe</a><meta itemprop="keywords" content="Angelo Linzalata, Coro Schola Cantorum San Gregorio Magno, Dario Argento, Dario Di Vietri, dimitra theodossiou, Elena Bianchini, Ernesto Petti, Giuseppe Altomare, Giuseppe Sabbatini, Giuseppe Verdi, Macbeth, Mauro Rolfi, Opera lirica, Orchestra Filarmonica del Piemonte, Piero Ceffa, Radu Pintillie, teatro Coccia di Novara, Valeria Sepe"> </span> </footer></div> </article><div id="author-block" class="box-shadow-2px clearfix" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"><h2 class="author-title">About the author</h2><div id="author-avatar"> <img itemprop="image" style="display:none;" src="http://gravatar.com/avatar/b41b40d04cc32e3e4f904f051c19deec" alt="" /> <img src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/Michele-Curnis-120x150.jpg" width="80" height="100" alt="Michele Curnis" class="avatar avatar-100 wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-100 alignnone photo" /></div><div id="author-description" class="padding-20"><meta itemprop="name" content="Michele Curnis"><meta itemprop="url" content=""><p></p><p class="add-author-info"> <a href="#"><i class="icon-facebook-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-twitter-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-google-plus-sign"></i></a></p> <a style="font-size: 11px;" href="http://www.gbopera.it/author/michele-curnis/">View all articles by Michele Curnis</a></div></div><div class="nav-block box-shadow-2px padding-20 clearfix"> <nav class="nav-single"><h3 class="assistive-text">Post navigation</h3> <span class="nav-previous"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2013/10/romaeuropa-festival-2013sfumato/" rel="prev"><span class="meta-nav">&larr;</span> Romaeuropa Festival 2013:&#8221;Sfumato&#8221;</a></span> <span class="nav-next"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2013/10/la-nuova-giselle-di-mancini-per-maggiodanza/" rel="next">La nuova &#8220;Giselle&#8221; di Mancini per MaggioDanza <span class="meta-nav">&rarr;</span></a></span> </nav><nav class="nav-single-hidden"> <span class="nav-previous"></span> <span class="nav-next"></span><div class="clear"></div> </nav></div><div class="comme